question_text:
Question 26 
 
  
[Complier Design (Parsing Techniques)] 
 
Which of the following is/are Bottom-Up Parser(s) ?.  
(A)
 
Shift - reduce Parser   
(B) Predictive Parser 
(C) LL(1) Parser 
(D) LR Parser 
Ans.  (A, D)
explanation_text:
Sol.
 
LR parser and shift-reduce parsers are bottom up parsers.
Hence, the correct option is (A) and (D).
